name: Jungle Rush
description:
Jungle Rush is a 30 second plat-former game where the objective is to complete levels before the 30 seconds run out of time!

Instructions

Controls -
[ A ] and [ D ] - to move left and right
[ W ] - to jump 
Vine Mechanics:
The player will automatically hook on to vines
[ Spacebar ] - to jump off vines

Objective:
Get to the end before 30 seconds!
Make sure to dodge enemies and not to fall into the lava!
